7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">المساحة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">٨٬١٢٥ م²</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">حالة الأصل</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">متاح للدراسة</p></article></div><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center rounded-md bg-[#A7815E] px-7 text-sm font-extrabold text-white\" href=\"/request-study\">طلب خدمة عقارية</a><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white px-7 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C]\" aria-busy=\"false\" aria-pressed=\"false\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg>اهتمام بالأصل</button></div></div></div><section class=\"mt-8 grid items-center gap-6 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_0.8fr]\"><div class=\"text-right\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">نبذة عن الأصل</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\">أرض سكنية تقع في شمال مدينة الرياض ضمن نطاق عمراني نام وقريب من الطرق الرئيسية والخدمات الحيوية.<!-- --> يتميز الموقع بقربه من المناطق الحيوية، مما يمنح الأصل مرونة في فرص التطوير السكني أو الاستثماري وفق دراسة منظمة تراعي المتطلبات النظامية.</p></div><div class=\"relative h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-surface\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale-[8%] sepia-[8%]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"35vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></section><section class=\"mt-7\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-right font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">معلومات الأصل</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-6\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">حالة الأصل</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">متاح</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2 mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m21 3-7 7\"></path><path d=\"m3 21 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M9 21H3v-6\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">الواجهة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">شمالية</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">المساحة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">٨٬١٢٥ م²</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">الحي</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">حي الياسمين</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">المدينة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">الرياض</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-house mx-auto h-9 w-9 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8\"></path><path d=\"M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528