\"/><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 h-10 w-10 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 fill-[#A7815E] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div></section><section class=\"mt-7\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-center font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916] gold-divider\">إمكانية التطوير</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-handshake mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m11 17 2 2a1 1 0 1 0 3-3\"></path><path d=\"m14 14 2.5 2.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3l-3.88-3.88a3 3 0 0 0-4.24 0l-.88.88a1 1 0 1 1-3-3l2.81-2.81a5.79 5.79 0 0 1 7.06-.87l.47.28a2 2 0 0 0 1.42.25L21 4\"></path><path d=\"m21 3 1 11h-2\"></path><path d=\"M3 3 2 14l6.5 6.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3\"></path><path d=\"M3 4h8\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">إمكانية التحويل لمساهمة عقارية</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold leading-7 text-muted\">إمكانية هيكلة الأصل وتحويله إلى مساهمة عقارية منظمة.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-store mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 21v-5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v5\"></path><path d=\"M17.774 10.31a1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.549 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.451 0 1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.548 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.452 0 1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.549 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.77-3.248l2.889-4.184A2 2 0 0 1 7 2h10a2 2 0 0 1 1.653.873l2.895 4.192a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.774 3.244\"></path><path d=\"M4 10.95V19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-8.05\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">فرصة استثمار</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold leading-7 text-muted\">إمكانية تحقيق عوائد استثمارية مجزية من خلال التطوير أو البيع.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">فرصة تطوير</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold leading-7 text-muted\">إمكانية تطوير الأصل لمشروع سكني متكامل يلبي الطلب.</p></article></div></section><section class=\"mt-7\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-center font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916] gold-divider\">الخدمات المرتبطة بالأصل</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square-text mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2