nt-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">أرض خام بالدمام</h3><p class=\"mt-1 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-3 w-3 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>الدمام</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold text-muted\">المساحة <span class=\"text-[#1D1916]\">١٢٬٠٠٠ م²</span></p><a class=\"mt-3 inline-flex h-8 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-[#A7815E]/45 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"/assets/dammam-raw-land\">عرض التفاصيل</a></div></article></div></section></div></section><section class=\"pb-7 pt-3\"><div class=\"landing-container\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line bg-[#f7f2ec] px-5 py-6 shadow-card md:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(8px);transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0\"><img alt=\"رسم معماري لأصل عقاري\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain object-left-bottom opacity-95 grayscale-[8%] sepia-[8%]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimag